<pb facs="1079380" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Illustrissimo ac Celeberrimo Viro
             <lb/>Joanni <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoullj</rs>
<lb/>Petrus Antonius <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelottus</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p>Jamdiu est quod bonatissimi tui Filii <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Danielis</rs> in hanc
         <lb/>civitatem adventum frustra expecto. Quidnam causae
         <lb/>fuerit quod ipse clarissimus tuus <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filius</rs> in <choice><orig>Jtaliam</orig><reg><rs key="place_KON-italie" type="place">Italiam</rs></reg></choice>
<lb/>nostram nondum advenerit, a Te, Amicissime Vir,
         <lb/>scire aveo; quanquam eum fortasse hac de re ali<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>quando ad me scripturum spero. Clarissimum
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jac. Jurinum</rs> <rs type="organisation">Regiae Societati Londinensi</rs> a Secretis,
         <lb/>humanissimas ad me dedisse <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">litteras</rs>, a modo me<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>morato summae virtutis tuo <rs key="" type="person">Filio</rs>, Te fieri certiorem
         <lb/>ante mensem circiter curavi, quidque ad me scripserit
         <lb/>idem <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jurinus</rs> indicavi. In praesentia vero Tibi, Sapien<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tissime Vir, significo me ipsimet <choice><abbr>Praeclariss</abbr><expan>Praeclarissimo</expan></choice> <rs key="" type="person">Jurino</rs>
<lb/>jam respondisse, rescripturumque quid de suis
         <lb/>in tuam ingeniosissam. de velocitatae aquae per
         <lb/>foramen vasis effluentis demonstrationem ani<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>madversionibus, ego vicissim sentiam, vel po<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tius Te sentire putem, spopondisse. Statim ac
         <lb/>Animadversiones Jurinianas accepero Te faciam
         <lb/>certiorem.</p> <closer><salute>Tu interim fac ut valeas, meque ama<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>re (quod vehementer opto) pergas.</salute>
<dateline><choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Dabam</expan></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1723-04-16">16. Aprilis 1723</date>.</dateline> </closer>
<pb facs="1079381" n="2"/>
<!-- figurtag -->
<postscript><p>P. S. </p>
<p>Aquae de vase cylindrico <formula>ABE</formula> per foramen <formula>EF</formula> effluen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tis tempore dato <formula>t</formula>, quantitatem non maiorem esse quantitate
            <lb/>ejusdem aquae in cylindro <formula>AE</formula> contentae probare
            <lb/>conatus fuit Praestantissimus tuus Filius <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Daniel</rs>
<lb/><rs key="B_1723-01-16_991170430253405501" type="letter">litteris 16. Januarii ad me perscriptis</rs>. Illis enim
            <lb/>ipsis litteris cylindrum aqueum <formula>ST</formula> eadem ratione
            <lb/>longitudine superare cylindrum <formula>AF</formula>, ac ab hoc
            <lb/>latitudine superatur, ideoque hos duos cylindros
            <lb/>aqueos aequales esse inter se, demonstrare alla<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>boravit. Dixit ergo quod guttulae <formula>F</formula>, <formula>Q</formula>, <formula>N</formula>, <formula>P</formula>, conflu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>unt (propterea quod aqua non est fluidissima) at<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>que hac ratione eas cylindrulum tenuiorem, seu gra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ciliorem <formula>ST</formula> constituere. Ego autem ut Cylin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>drum aqueum <formula>FM</formula> longiorem esse cylindro <formula>AF</formula> eandem
            <lb/>cum illo basim habente (posita aquae summa
            <lb/>fluiditate) libenter do sic aquae guttulis
            <lb/><formula>F</formula>, <formula>Q</formula>, <formula>N</formula>, <formula>P</formula> confluentibus, sive magis ad se accedenti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>bus graciliorem evadere cylindrum <formula>FM</formula>, non
            <lb/>clare intelligo; mihi potius videtur ipsum
            <pb facs="1079382"/>
<lb/>cylindrum <formula>FM</formula> confluentibus aquae guttulis <formula>F</formula>, <formula>Q</formula>, <formula>N</formula>, <formula>P</formula>,
            <lb/>breviorem fieri debere; ideo enim longior esset quia
            <lb/>interstitiola remanerent posita summa
            <lb/>aquae fluiditate. propter <choice><sic>aequalitem</sic><corr>aequalitatem</corr></choice> actionis, et
            <lb/>retroactionis guttularum aquae per foramen <formula>EF</formula>
<lb/>egredientium. Ego ut hujusmodi meam difficulta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tem examines, quidve de ea Tibi videatur,
            <lb/>ad me scribere ne graveris etiam atque
            <lb/>etiam rogo, ac quaeso, Vale iterum, Illustrissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>me Vir, Filiumque tuum aliquando ad me mitte. </p></postscript>
